<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Character on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/character/</link><description>Recent content in Character on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/character/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] Perl Encoding Error Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/perl/perl-encoding-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/perl/perl-encoding-error/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An encoding error occurs when Perl cannot handle character encoding properly. This can happen when mixing byte strings and character strings, or when reading files with wrong encoding.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mixing bytes and characters&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Wrong encoding declaration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;File read with wrong encoding&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Output encoding mismatch&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-perl" data-lang="perl"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# WRONG: Not declaring encoding&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;use&lt;/span&gt; strict;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;use&lt;/span&gt; warnings;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# No encoding handling&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# CORRECT: Enable UTF-8&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;use&lt;/span&gt; strict;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;use&lt;/span&gt; warnings;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;use&lt;/span&gt; utf8;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;binmode(STDOUT, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;:utf8&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-perl" data-lang="perl"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# WRONG: Reading file without encoding&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;open(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;my&lt;/span&gt; $fh, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;lt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;data.txt&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;my&lt;/span&gt; $text &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;lt;$fh&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# May be bytes&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# CORRECT: Read with encoding&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;open(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;my&lt;/span&gt; $fh, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;lt;:encoding(UTF-8)&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;data.txt&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;my&lt;/span&gt; $text &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;lt;$fh&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-perl" data-lang="perl"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Example 1: UTF-8 handling&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;use&lt;/span&gt; utf8;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;use&lt;/span&gt; open IO &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;:std, :encoding(UTF-8)&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;my&lt;/span&gt; $text &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Hello, World!&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Example 2: Encode/Decode&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;use&lt;/span&gt; Encode;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;my&lt;/span&gt; $bytes &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; encode(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;UTF-8&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, $text);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;my&lt;/span&gt; $chars &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; decode(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;UTF-8&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, $bytes);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Example 3: File encoding&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;open(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;my&lt;/span&gt; $fh, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;lt;:encoding(ISO-8859-1)&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;latin1.txt&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;while&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;lt;$fh&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;print&lt;/span&gt; $_; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Output in UTF-8&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="perl-unicode-error"&gt;Perl unicode error&lt;/a&gt; - Unicode issue&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="perl-file-not-found"&gt;Perl file not found&lt;/a&gt; - file not found&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="perl-runtime-error"&gt;Perl runtime error&lt;/a&gt; - runtime issue&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] Perl Unicode Error Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/perl/perl-unicode-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/perl/perl-unicode-error/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A Unicode error occurs when Perl cannot handle Unicode characters properly. This can happen with string operations, comparisons, or output of multi-byte characters.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;String treated as bytes instead of characters&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Wrong Unicode normalization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Output encoding mismatch&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Regex on Unicode strings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-perl" data-lang="perl"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# WRONG: Treating Unicode as bytes&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;use&lt;/span&gt; utf8;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;my&lt;/span&gt; $text &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Hello&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# May be bytes&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# CORRECT: Proper UTF-8 handling&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;use&lt;/span&gt; utf8;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;use&lt;/span&gt; open IO &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;:std, :encoding(UTF-8)&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;my&lt;/span&gt; $text &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Hello&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-perl" data-lang="perl"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# WRONG: Wrong comparison&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;my&lt;/span&gt; $a &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;\x{00E9}&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# e with accent&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;my&lt;/span&gt; $b &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;e\x{0301}&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# e + combining accent&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; ($a &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;eq&lt;/span&gt; $b) { &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Different byte sequences&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;print&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Equal\n&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# CORRECT: Normalize before comparison&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;use&lt;/span&gt; Unicode::Normalize;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (NFC($a) &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;eq&lt;/span&gt; NFC($b)) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;print&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Equal\n&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-perl" data-lang="perl"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Example 1: Unicode strings&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;use&lt;/span&gt; utf8;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;my&lt;/span&gt; $text &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Hello, World!&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;print&lt;/span&gt; length($text); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Character count, not byte count&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Example 2: Unicode regex&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; ($text &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=~&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt; /\p{Letter}+/&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;print&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Contains letters\n&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Example 3: Unicode file reading&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;open(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;my&lt;/span&gt; $fh, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;lt;:encoding(UTF-8)&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;unicode.txt&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;while&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;lt;$fh&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;print&lt;/span&gt; $_;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="perl-encoding-error"&gt;Perl encoding error&lt;/a&gt; - encoding issue&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="perl-regexp-error"&gt;Perl regexp error&lt;/a&gt; - regex issue&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="perl-runtime-error"&gt;Perl runtime error&lt;/a&gt; - runtime issue&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] String: conversion from cell to string error in MATLAB</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/matlab/matlab-string-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/matlab/matlab-string-error/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;MATLAB string errors occur when converting between cell arrays of character vectors, string arrays, and character arrays. Different representations require different conversion methods.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mixing cell and string types&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Invalid character encoding&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Empty cells in conversion&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mismatched dimensions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Using wrong conversion function&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-matlab" data-lang="matlab"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;% WRONG: Direct assignment type mismatch&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;cellArray = {&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;hello&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;world&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;};
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;strArray = string(cellArray); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;% May cause issues&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;% CORRECT: Proper conversion&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;cellArray = {&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;hello&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;world&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;};
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;strArray = string(cellArray); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;% Explicit conversion&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-matlab" data-lang="matlab"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;% WRONG: Converting empty cell&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;cellArray = {&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;hello&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;world&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;};
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;strArray = string(cellArray); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;% May create missing entries&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;% CORRECT: Handle empty cells&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;cellArray = {&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;hello&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;world&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;};
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;strArray = string(cellArray);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;strArray(strtrim(strArray) &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;==&lt;/span&gt; &amp;#34;&amp;#34;) = missing; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;% Mark as missing&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-matlab" data-lang="matlab"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;% CORRECT: Conversion methods&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;% Cell to string&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;cellArr = {&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;a&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;b&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;c&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;};
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;strArr = string(cellArr);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;% String to cell&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;cellArr = cellstr(strArr);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;% Character vector to string&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;charVec = &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;hello&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;str = string(charVec);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;% String to character&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;charVec = char(strArr);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-matlab" data-lang="matlab"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;% CORRECT: Validate before conversion&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; strArr = &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;safeConvert&lt;/span&gt;(input)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; iscell(input)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; strArr = string(input);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;elseif&lt;/span&gt; ischar(input) &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;||&lt;/span&gt; isstring(input)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; strArr = string(input);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;else&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; error(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;Unsupported input type&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-matlab" data-lang="matlab"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;% CORRECT: Handle mixed types&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;data = {&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;text&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;42&lt;/span&gt;, true};
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;strArr = strings(size(data));
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; i = &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;:numel(data)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; strArr(i) = string(data{i});
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="matlab-table-error"&gt;Table Error&lt;/a&gt; - variable access&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="matlab-undefined-function-v2"&gt;Undefined Function&lt;/a&gt; - function errors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="matlab-index-out-of-range-v2"&gt;Index Out of Range&lt;/a&gt; - array bounds&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] Swift Error — String Index Is Out of Bounds</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/swift/string-index/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/swift/string-index/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="string-index-is-out-of-bounds"&gt;String Index Is Out of Bounds&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This error occurs when you access a &lt;code&gt;String.Index&lt;/code&gt; that is not within the valid range of the string&amp;rsquo;s characters. String indices in Swift are not integers, making this error more subtle than array index errors.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Swift strings store characters using UTF-8 encoding internally. A &lt;code&gt;String.Index&lt;/code&gt; is an opaque type, not a simple integer. You cannot use integer subscripts directly on strings. Attempting to advance an index beyond the string&amp;rsquo;s bounds, or using an index from a different string, causes this crash.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Invalid character in name</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/haskell/invalid-continuation/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/haskell/invalid-continuation/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An &lt;code&gt;Invalid character in name&lt;/code&gt; error occurs when you use characters that aren&amp;rsquo;t allowed in Haskell identifiers. Haskell has specific rules about what characters can appear in variable and type names.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Using special characters in identifiers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Unicode characters in code&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reserved words used as identifiers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Invalid operator characters&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-haskell" data-lang="haskell"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- WRONG: Invalid character in identifier&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;my&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;var &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;10&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Invalid character: -&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- CORRECT: Use valid characters&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;myVar&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-haskell" data-lang="haskell"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- WRONG: Using reserved word&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;data&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; [&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- &amp;#39;data&amp;#39; is reserved&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- CORRECT: Use different name&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;myData&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; [&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-haskell" data-lang="haskell"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Example 1: Hyphen in name&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;my&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;function &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;10&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Invalid character&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Example 2: Special character&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;var&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;@&lt;/span&gt;name &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;10&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Invalid character: @&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Example 3: Unicode&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;café&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;coffee&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- may cause issues in some compilers&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/haskell/variable-not-in-scope"&gt;Variable not in scope&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/haskell/ghc-error"&gt;GHC compilation error&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>